<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Ey Ota</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ey Ota, madx, iyam Senga
 Taxtingni oldida
 Shukurlar aytib
 Ulugʻlayman Seni.
 Iso qimmatli Sen menga
 Senga tengdosh xech kim yuq
 Faqat Sen loyiqsan
 Sen loyiqsan, madx, iyamga

[C1]
   // Ofarin Senga Ofarin Senga
   Ofarin Senga
   Rabbiy Iso //

[C2]
   Sevaman Seni, Sevaman Seni
   Sevaman Seni, Rabbiy Iso

[C3]
   Madx, iyam Senga
   Madx, iyam Senga
   Madx, iyam Senga
   Rabbiy Iso</lyrics>
<title>Ofarin Senga</title>
</song>